{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1013865, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 202130, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "姓从存在开始就是父权标志啊喂，有本事直接废了姓", "timestamp": 1611916793, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1013866, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 202130, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "传统就是这样，不这样的话每次都要和别人解释一下", "timestamp": 1611916795, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1013873, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 202130, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "首先，应该这个词成不成立还不知道嗷", "timestamp": 1611916841, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1013878, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 202130, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "换句话说，如果不是父系传承，那就是一般意义的姓了（，在这个基础上跟女方姓本身就是被赋予了特别意义的异常情况，当然不愿意", "timestamp": 1611916852, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1013882, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 202130, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "就跟清华大学改名成清华小学，但是还颁发本科学位一样，你愿意吗（", "timestamp": 1611916875, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1013891, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 202130, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "还好我npy和我同姓", "timestamp": 1611916955, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1013894, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 202130, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 针对这么认为的男生哈", "timestamp": 1611916975, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1013897, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 202130, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "因为我是孩他爹，", "timestamp": 1611916984, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1013903, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 202130, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "大多是因为怕其他人指指点点", "timestamp": 1611917027, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1013904, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 202130, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 啊，第二句应该是“那就不是一般意义的姓了”", "timestamp": 1611917034, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1013907, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 202130, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "所以有谁想过为什么姓会存在呢?", "timestamp": 1611917054, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1013927, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 202130, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 清华小学我真的无所谓...清华就是清华，本质不变啊。既然你说姓是父权标志且认为应该保留这个传统，那么你是认同父权制度的吗？", "timestamp": 1611917186, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1013938, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 202130, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 那孩它妈为什么没有冠姓权呢", "timestamp": 1611917227, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1013944, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 202130, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 是啊，但是这种异常的事情存在会恶心一部分人，，", "timestamp": 1611917276, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1013946, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 202130, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 因为别的孩他爹都有冠姓权，别的孩他妈都没有", "timestamp": 1611917285, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1013951, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 202130, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 比如隔壁还是大学，全中国都是大学，就一个清华小学，那绝对会被冲烂，，", "timestamp": 1611917312, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1013952, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 202130, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 你非得叫孩子跟你姓 说出去我很尴尬啊", "timestamp": 1611917312, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1013965, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 202130, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Bob和Francis说出了我作为女性也无心去争所谓冠姓权的主要原因：感觉不到什么好处，反而还会带来一堆麻烦", "timestamp": 1611917399, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1013971, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 202130, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 我不认同啊，但是我觉得姓氏制度作为一个可以独立于父权制存在的文化现象，其去留很难用纯粹的理性推导决定，更多还是看历史的惯性吧。你看要是真的男女之间毫无实质的利益矛盾了，那其实姓氏作为无害的历史现象没有反对其存在的理由，自然的延续下去不是不可能的事情吧?", "timestamp": 1611917418, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1013989, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 202130, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "没有为什么，因为我将会在我的家庭里占据主导地位", "timestamp": 1611917533, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1014020, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 202130, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我还是很支持子女姓里面父母姓氏都加进去", "timestamp": 1611917666, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1014036, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 202130, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 所以就是从众心理咯？", "timestamp": 1611917728, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1014050, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 202130, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 所以是“拳头说话”的类似心理吗", "timestamp": 1611917806, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1014066, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 202130, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 我暂不讨论它作为文化现象的去留，而且现在男女间的利益矛盾还挺明显的，而且很难说它是无害的吧。我更想知道你个人认为应该随父姓的逻辑基础", "timestamp": 1611917918, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1014154, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 202130, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 差不多吧，我眼里是天经地义的事情，如果我对象能提供更好的物质条件，我愿意孩子跟她姓，但我大概率不会找这样的对象", "timestamp": 1611918400, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1014274, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 202130, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 也算逻辑自洽，没毛病", "timestamp": 1611919213, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 2, "pid": 202130, "reply": 26, "tag": null, "text": "#202126\n想问问男生们为什么认为孩子应该随自己的姓？", "timestamp": 1611916738, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1611919211, "url": "", "vote": {}}}